<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NextLevel Design | 音が鳴る完全版LP</title>
    
    <style>
        /* ==========================================================================
           1. 画面全体の基本的なお約束（ベースCSS）
           ========================================================================== */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth; /* ボタンを押したときにスーッと動く魔法のCSS */
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Hiragino Kaku Gothic ProN', Meiryo, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.9;
            color: #2c3e50;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
            transition: background 0.3s, color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 4%;
        }

        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #0f172a;
        }

        .title-underline {
            width: 70px;
            height: 5px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #0076ff, #00c6ff);
            margin: 0 auto 40px;
            border-radius: 3px;
        }

        .section-subtitle {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #64748b;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto 60px;
        }

        /* ==========================================================================
           2. ヘッダー（画面の上のメニューバー）のCSS
           ========================================================================== */
        header {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.97);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .header-inner {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            height: 90px;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #0076ff, #00c6ff);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 35px;
            list-style: none;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: #0076ff;
        }

        .cta-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0076ff 0%, #0056b3 100%);
            color: #fff !important;
            padding: 12px 28px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .cta-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 118, 255, 0.4);
        }

        /* ==========================================================================
           3. ヒーロー（画面最初の大きな暗いエリア）のCSS
           ========================================================================== */
        .hero {
            background: radial-gradient(circle at top right, #1e3a8a, #0f172a);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 160px 0 140px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .hero-title {
            font-size: 4rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1.4;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .hero-title span {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #38bdf8, #34d399);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .hero-lead {
            font-size: 1.35rem;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto 50px;
            color: #cbd5e1;
        }

        .hero-action {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff5e62 0%, #ff9966 100%);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 18px 45px;
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 50px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(255, 94, 98, 0.4);
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .hero-action:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(255, 94, 98, 0.6);
        }

        /* ==========================================================================
           4. サービス紹介のCSS
           ========================================================================== */
        .services {
            padding: 120px 0;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .services-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(340px, 1fr));
            gap: 40px;
        }

        .service-card {
            padding: 50px 40px;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .service-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        /* ==========================================================================
           5. 特長セクションのCSS
           ========================================================================== */
        .features {
            padding: 120px 0;
            background-color: #f1f5f9;
        }

        .feature-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 80px;
            margin-bottom: 100px;
        }

        .feature-img-box {
            flex: 1;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e2e8f0 0%, #cbd5e1 100%);
            height: 400px;
            border-radius: 24px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #475569;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .feature-text-box {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .feature-tag {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #e0f2fe;
            color: #0369a1;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        /* ==========================================================================
           6. お問い合わせフォームのCSS
           ========================================================================== */
        .contact-section {
            padding: 120px 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #e2e8f0 100%);
        }

        .contact-card {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 60px 50px;
            border-radius: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #0f172a;
        }

        .form-control {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px 18px;
            border: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #334155;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
        }

        .submit-btn {
            width: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff5e62 0%, #ff7b54 100%);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 18px;
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(255, 94, 98, 0.3);
        }

        /* ==========================================================================
           7. スマホ用レスポンシブ
           ========================================================================== */
        @media (max-width: 992px) {
            .feature-row {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 40px;
            }
            .feature-img-box {
                width: 100%;
                height: 300px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <audio id="idiot-sound" src="https://www.myinstants.com/media/sounds/you-are-an-idiot-42738.mp3" preload="auto"></audio>

    <header>
        <div class="container header-inner">
            <div class="logo">NextLevel Design</div>
            <nav>
                <ul class="nav-links">
                    <li><a href="#services">提供サービス</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#features">私たちの強み</a></li>
                    <li><button onclick="document.getElementById('contact').scrollIntoView({behavior: 'smooth'});" class="cta-btn" style="border:none; cursor:pointer;">無料相談はこちら</button></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="container">
                <h1 class="hero-title">デザインと最先端技術で、<br><span>ビジネスを次のステージへ。</span></h1>
                <p class="hero-lead">NextLevel Designは、単に美しいWebサイトを作るだけの会社ではありません。お客様の本質的な経営課題に向き合い、最新のWebテクノロジーを融合させるプロフェッショナル集団です。</p>
                <button onclick="document.getElementById('contact').scrollIntoView({behavior: 'smooth'});" class="hero-action" style="border:none;">無料で今すぐ相談してみる</button>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="services" class="services">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title">提供する多角的なWebソリューション</h2>
                <div class="title-underline"></div>
                <div class="services-grid">
                    <div class="service-card">
                        <div class="service-icon">💻</div>
                        <h3>次世代コーポレートサイト制作</h3>
                        <p>企業の「顔」であるコーポレートサイトは、信頼性を担保するだけでなく、攻めの営業ツールでなければなりません。私たちは、競合他社の徹底的なリサーチからスタートし、貴社の独自の強み（USP）を視覚的に伝える最先端のデザインを提供します。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-card">
                        <div class="service-icon">🛒</div>
                        <h3>売上最大化ECサイト・通販システム</h3>
                        <p>現代のECビジネスにおいて、サイトの使いやすさは売上に直結します。私たちは、Shopifyをはじめとする世界標準のECプラットフォームを活用し、お客様のビジネス規模や商材に最適なオンラインストアを構築します。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="features" class="features">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title">私たちが市場で圧倒的に選ばれる理由</h2>
                <div class="title-underline"></div>
                <div class="feature-row">
                    <div class="feature-img-box">【ビジネス理解の深化】</div>
                    <div class="feature-text-box">
                        <span class="feature-tag">REASON 01</span>
                        <h3>経営課題の核心に迫る、超深層カウンセリングと市場調査</h3>
                        <p>多くの制作会社は、お客様から言われた要件をそのまま形にします。しかし、私たちは違います。プロジェクトのスタート時には、お客様の業界動向、競合他社のWeb戦略まで徹底的にリサーチします。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="contact" class="contact-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title">無料相談・お問い合わせ</h2>
                <div class="title-underline"></div>
                <div class="contact-card">
                    <form onsubmit="event.preventDefault(); document.getElementById('idiot-sound').play(); alert('You are an idiot! ♪ 音楽と一緒にポップアップが出たよ！');">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="name">お名前 <span>必須</span></label>
                            <input type="text" id="name" class="form-control" placeholder="例：山田 太郎" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="email">メールアドレス <span>必須</span></label>
                            <input type="email" id="email" class="form-control" placeholder="例：example@nextlevel.com" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="message">ご相談内容 <span>必須</span></label>
                            <textarea id="message" class="form-control" placeholder="例：ホームページの相談です" required></textarea>
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">この内容で無料相談を申し込む</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer style="background-color: #0f172a; color: #94a3b8; padding: 40px 0; text-align: center;">
        <p>&copy; 2026 NextLevel Design. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
